#

Chipotle Turkey Burger

25 min
$12
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Gluten (if using regular buns)

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

EasyQuickProtein-Packed

Description

A smoky, spicy turkey burger with a kick, served juicy and flavorful, perfect for a quick meal!

Ingredients

  • ground turkey: 1 pound
  • chipotle sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • onion powder: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • burger buns: 4
  • lettuce leaves: 4
  • tomato slices: 8
  • cheddar cheese (optional): 4 slices
